  "env_id": "vtiger_crm_env@0.1",
  "description": "You need to update 10 existing contact records in the Vtiger CRM using the bulk import tool with data provided in '/home/ga/Documents/enriched_contacts.csv'. Perform the update by matching existing records based on 'Primary Email' to prevent duplicate creation. Map the CSV columns 'First Name', 'Last Name', 'Email', 'Title', and 'Direct Phone' to the CRM fields First Name, Last Name, Primary Email, Title, and Office Phone respectively. Ensure the records are updated successfully without increasing the total number of contacts in the system.",
